'''rdiff-backup''' is a GPL-licensed incremental backup utility based on the [[rsync]] command. It is able to store changes to files instead of file duplicates therefore reducing storage requirements. Incremental data can be viewed and restored as if it were whole a file backup via [[FUSE]]-based <tt>rdiff-backup-fs</tt>.

